Name: Slime Age: Parody MMORPG Clicker
About the game: The slime era has arrived! Slimes have captured all locations and hold valuable loot for adventurers! Which slime catches your fancy? Classic pink, slime-dog, or cat slime? Or perhaps slime-panda? Collect loot, uncover endearing characters, and explore locations in this clicker game parody. A game for people who like slimes and cute catgirls!
